OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDalai Lama regrets asking  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fboy to 'suck my tongue'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Dalai Lama has apologised after    
OL,6, footage showed him asking a boy if he  
OL,7, wanted to suck the Tibetan spiritual   
OL,8, leader's tongue.                       
OL,10,FHis office said he wanted to apologise 
OL,11,Fto the child and his family "for the   
OL,12,Fhurt his words may have caused".       
OL,14,FThe video also shows the Dalai Lama    
OL,15,Fkissing the child on his lips.         
OL,17,F"His Holiness often teases people he   
OL,18,Fmeets in an innocent and playful way,  
OL,19,Feven in public and before cameras. He  
OL,20,Fregrets the incident," his office said.
